title: Frank Lloyd Wright Trivet—Saguaro Forms
description:
Based on the design Saguaro Forms and Cactus Flowers from an unpublished Liberty Magazine cover circa 1926-1927, this tabletop trivet features one of Frank Lloyd Wright’s® (American, 1867-1959) most enigmatic patterns. Made in the USA of absorbent stone with a surface protecting cork back.

7 in. square.
